{"tid":1495973,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"環時：英國領事館職員鄭文傑因嫖妓被拘留","createTime":"2019-08-22T09:52:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T05:45:47.000Z","uid":123688,"like":3,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"cc2e74f87aced9ad0a68fbf9ad144f767b4e0e36","tid":1495973,"uid":123688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T09:52:54.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】內地傳媒報道，被內地拘留的英國領事館香港職員，是因嫖妓被行政拘留。<br />\n<br />\n環球時報引述深圳羅湖公安指，鄭文傑因為嫖妓，被行政拘留15日。對於有質疑他被扣留後，當局未有通報其家屬，報道指公安是應當事人要求，依法未有把他的違法行為通報其家屬。<br />\n<br />\n羅湖公安又強調，中國是法治國家，任何人從事違法犯罪活動，都會受法律懲處。<br />\n<br />\n28歲的鄭文傑Simon，是英國駐港總領事館職員。他的家人報稱他本月8日由香港往深圳公幹，晚上乘搭高鐵返港，約晚上十時告知女友正在過關，其後失去聯絡，英國外交部表示強烈關注。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=360071&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D360071%26refer%3D&d=MOEBQbH5BhSBv0g7AWUGIWLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=aed14c90\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D360071%26refer%3D&h=12cb33ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=360071&amp;refer=</a>"},{"pid":"170b5586f4e6027d870c25876577a510a5ccf508","tid":1495973,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T09:59:12.000Z","msg":"新湯渣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40ed57a979b1c7b16d4a5a6bbe27d0f77711ec89","tid":1495973,"uid":96512,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T09:59:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/-8XrDEVK-jVE/VYASHgtfeOI/AAAAAAAAd14/gcdooJukQ9k/w1598-h898-no/IMG_1434455322696.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh6.googleusercontent.com%2F-8XrDEVK-jVE%2FVYASHgtfeOI%2FAAAAAAAAd14%2FgcdooJukQ9k%2Fw1598-h898-no%2